On Saturday, July 23, 2005, at 02:44PM, Rob <becida(-at-)comcast.net> wrote:

>Will a 1600 drop into a later (72 or 73) bus?

You will need some european engine tin or the fiberglass substitute from Creative Car Craft and you will need to modify the engine support bar. If you've got a universal case you won't have to drill the case to adapt it to the mounting bar.

http://www.busdepot.com/details.jsp?partnumber=BD101G
http://www.creativecarcraft.com/notforbug.htm

